{"id":"kelita","term":"Kelita","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Dwarf, a Levite who assisted Ezra in expounding the law to the people (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Nehemiah 8:7\">Neh. 8:7</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Nehemiah 10:10\">10:10</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Nehemiah 8:7","Nehemiah 10:10"]}